# NAME

**@MCCODE_PREFIX@doc** - Creating and viewing the @MCCODE_NAME@ library, component/instrument help and
Manuals

# SYNOPSIS

**@MCCODE_PREFIX@doc** [-h] [--install] [--dir DIR] [--manual] [--comps] [--web] [--verbose] [searchterm]

# DESCRIPTION

The **@MCCODE_PREFIX@doc** front-end generates html docpages from @MCCODE_NAME@ instrument and
component files. A docpage is generated for every instrument and component
file, and an overview page is written and browsed. Just type `@MCCODE_PREFIX@plot`.

# OPTIONS

**searchterm**
:   search filter or .instr/.comp file

**-h, --help**
:   show this help message and exit

**--install, -i**
:   generate installation master doc page

**--dir DIR, -d DIR**
:   add search results from this directory

**--manual, -m**
:   open the system manual

**--comps, -c**
:   open the component manual

**--web, -w**
:   open the @FLAVOR@ website

**--verbose, -v**
:   prints a parsing log during execution

